        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 895.7365365505144,
        "end": 905.0565365505145
      },
      {
        "id": "19648472-41e5-4aaa-8339-01b0233458cd",
        "text": "て いうのじゃない。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 941.5198635482714,
        "end": 942.4798735482714
      },
      {
        "id": "1da30b68-d282-478e-bb64-460e7b44bc13",
        "text": "家しか 決してにさフラリカフェあるじゃん 潰れた 知ら ん。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 958.7799271964973,
        "end": 1015.8475816154444
      },
      {
        "id": "5f1ac5d4-e4c4-486a-9bdf-a8c05f111cae",
        "text": "。だって明日から出店するかもしれなかった 出店しないとこうとは思ってたけど",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1029.3739550018302,
        "end": 1035.0539550018302
      },
      {
        "id": "201b32a4-0ab2-465b-979b-6f35876c7f2a",
        "text": "",
        "speaker_id": 2,
        "speaker_name": "Speaker 2",
        "start": 1039.0139550018303,
        "end": 1039.6539450018302
      },
      {
        "id": "b23b50cf-6293-45db-bcfd-ef4a55f8a8c5",
        "text": "千百万ぐらいかけてこのタイミング で敗退だから 多分二千万ぐらいキャッシュを 減ってると思う 。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1039.6539450018302,
        "end": 1046.97395500183
      },
      {
        "id": "c3f683c7-d26e-4830-a440-ac31307b0ed8",
        "text": "倒れそう であれだったかだよね。",
        "speaker_id": 0,
        "speaker_name": "りえ",
        "start": 1048.5339550018302,
        "end": 1049.8939550018301
      },
      {
        "id": "7d0691c3-de5f-4ca0-a081-49ff14bae29b",
        "text": "だね、確かに。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1050.97395500183,
        "end": 1057.3439550018302
      },
      {
        "id": "441c5927-9daa-40af-9dbf-3e4839a90e0c",
        "text": "意外では 外ではあるね。割と良かったけどね、雰囲気とか。",
        "speaker_id": 2,
        "speaker_name": "Speaker 2",
        "start": 1057.3439550018302,
        "end": 1057.50395500183
      },
      {
        "id": "dbd036c9-5505-41b3-a110-3cd17ba8f549",
        "text": "俺が何",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1067.1107027912203,
        "end": 1068.0707027912204
      },
      {
        "id": "f28257d1-397c-4f42-8035-cc3b6a87277f",
        "text": "",
        "speaker_id": 0,
        "speaker_name": "りえ",
        "start": 1068.4307027912203,
        "end": 1069.7107027912202
      },
      {
        "id": "79512246-a8a2-46c2-96da-57fe55b4415f",
        "text": "ジャミルミーだっ理由は。俺は何をやる?",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1069.7107027912202,
        "end": 1071.1507027912203
      },
      {
        "id": "6288bb5a-c5ac-4346-bf68-4187b19529ae",
        "text": "お金が無かったから。",
        "speaker_id": 0,
        "speaker_name": "りえ",
        "start": 1073.0707027912204,
        "end": 1074.1907027912202
      },
      {
        "id": "6240bd2e-193d-48a4-add9-725d29fec7f9",
        "text": "高かった普通に お金なかったのがあるね 他にも出店したい店舗あったからね。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1075.5507027912204,
        "end": 1083.5507027912204
      },
      {
        "id": "991987ae-b6c5-4ffe-9b17-ed406fc37f78",
        "text": "当てるのと向こうのが早かったってのは 悩んでいたら負けたみたい",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1088.9020579528917,
        "end": 1095.0020579528918
      },
      {
        "id": "b7feca62-5677-4051-8a38-42f31c0d110b",
        "text": "。まあでもやめようかなと思っ て",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1099.4020579528917,
        "end": 1101.5720679528918
      },
      {
        "id": "fbffe33b-200d-42ed-9837-2dc39b258a71",
        "text": "思って そしたら",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1115.0724925232075,
        "end": 1118.3925025232074
      },
      {
        "id": "055a7915-25db-4a1a-b790-bd872de32d92",
        "text": "ゲストに",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1149.4900312996033,
        "end": 1150.1300312996032
      },
      {
        "id": "667d872d-02ee-4ade-9cdf-45d036e95f8b",
        "text": "そう。",
        "speaker_id": 2,
        "speaker_name": "Speaker 2",
        "start": 1160.2300312996033,
        "end": 1160.5500512996032
      },
      {
        "id": "013f1dfd-6ebd-4ada-ac38-2e56635695e9",
        "text": "",
        "speaker_id": 0,
        "speaker_name": "りえ",
        "start": 1161.3300312996032,
        "end": 1162.2900112996033
      },
      {
        "id": "be59c2da-c5a4-4393-a41f-26ca2cef7265",
        "text": "はきつくないかきついね しかも多分フラリ",
        "speaker_id": 2,
        "speaker_name": "Speaker 2",
        "start": 1162.5300312996033,
        "end": 1163.1700112996032
      },
      {
        "id": "4fa0ba11-567d-4e0c-bde5-b114b8a1503a",
        "text": "セレカウルが安いんだよね。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1167.7700312996033,
        "end": 1169.3700312996032
      },
      {
        "id": "0c083c2e-d9a7-4fbc-a19e-4298532454e5",
        "text": "",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1207.1420678916086,
        "end": 1208.5820778916086
      },
      {
        "id": "1bdece22-9063-4fcc-a0b1-de094697d0b4",
        "text": "。絶対出展されんもん。",
        "speaker_id": 2,
        "speaker_name": "Speaker 2",
        "start": 1208.5820778916086,
        "end": 1208.8220678916086
      },
      {
        "id": "e5f889a6-be7c-4fc6-8114-afe63e4c2aa9",
        "text": "強豪に あんなとこ 池下はさ、まだやっぱ 多いじゃん、顧客が。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1208.9420478916086,
        "end": 1215.6620278916087
      },
      {
        "id": "cf2ab0c0-4123-4a31-8e47-95808cb32a4b",
        "text": "今 初めて使いますが、これどうやるのか教えてくだい。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1239.1399782562062,
        "end": 1242.259978256206
      },
      {
        "id": "91062b6d-59b8-4ecf-b4f2-6ddd1d31f9d6",
        "text": "How old are you?",
        "speaker_id": 99,
        "speaker_name": "Speaker 99",
        "start": 1301.7670447826385,
        "end": 1303.3670447826385
      },
      {
        "id": "c8a754ab-3c31-4ff8-97c8-8a10fb660893",
        "text": "八時半",
        "speaker_id": 0,
        "speaker_name": "りえ",
        "start": 1310.706114025116,
        "end": 1311.4261138251159
      },
      {
        "id": "338822b0-cebf-4628-9b48-ee7e11f615b5",
        "text": "車道。",
        "speaker_id": 0,
        "speaker_name": "りえ",
        "start": 1315.706114025116,
        "end": 1316.506114025116
      },
      {
        "id": "0ffe60ce-87f6-4264-af9b-59454b7d10a9",
        "text": "そんな音しゃかんで勝利。そんな音しゃじゃダじゃん。違う違う私とかじゃないか しゃえと。",
        "speaker_id": 0,
        "speaker_name": "りえ",
        "start": 1320.266114025116,
        "end": 1324.866114025116
      },
      {
        "id": "f13253c3-a1b9-45b1-9187-e8069d38dfbe",
        "text": "おしっこなんて絶対行けないじゃん。",
        "speaker_id": 1,
        "speaker_name": "User",
        "start": 1355.3049724388125,
        "end": 1357.5449724388125
      }
    ]
  },
  {
